<p>Her dreamy maroon eyes rolled toward the top of her long skull. She was staring at his fat blue lips. It was maybe she expected him to whistle the "Lost Chord." The rock on his finger exploded blue-white, frozen fireworks. He raised his glass to curse all square bitches. He was con-toasting all whores. The room got silent. Somebody had strangled the gold phonograph in the corner.</p>
<p>He toasted:</p>
<blockquote><p>Before I'd touch a square bitch's slit, I'd suck a thousand clappy pricks<sup><a href="#footnote_60_97332" id="identifier_60_97332" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="There is such a thing as pharingeal gonorheisis, so this isn't merely exaggeration. It'd come with its price tag.
